org.apache.commons.math4.analysis.integration

Class MidPointIntegratorTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.commons.math4.analysis.integration.MidPointIntegratorTest

  • public final class MidPointIntegratorTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Test case for midpoint integrator.

    Test runs show that for a default relative accuracy of 1E-6, it generally takes 10 to 15 iterations for the integral to converge.
